Class OVRTrackingState

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.lwjgl.system.PointerWrapper
      • org.lwjgl.system.Struct

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Pointer

    public class OVRTrackingState
extends Struct
    Tracking state at a given absolute time (describes predicted HMD pose etc). Returned by OVR#ovrHmd_GetTrackingState.
